  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-03 stale input data)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. The model was revised in early 2026 (modelRevisionDate 2026-02-01); however, the primary rheology dataset used to parameterise the hemolysis power-law model carries a dataVintage of 2025-09-15, predating the revision. Re-validation against the updated model build is noted as planned but has not been completed.",
