      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Bench-scale hemolysis validation against FDA pump experimental data",
      "description": "CFD-predicted hemolysis index compared against published FDA pump experimental measurements at 5 flow-speed operating points. Mean absolute error 12.4%; within the pre-specified 15% acceptance band. Monte Carlo UQ (500 samples) yields 90th-percentile prediction interval spanning ±18% of nominal HI."
    },
