      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must hold ISO 9001 certification and traceable regression-test suite covering hemolysis sub-model; version-controlled builds with release notes required.",
      "rationale": "Solver holds ISO 9001 certification and a regression-test suite exists, but the hemolysis sub-model unit tests were not updated following the February 2026 revision. Achieved level 3 against required level 4."
    },
