      "rationale": "Three-mesh Richardson extrapolation performed; GCI on hemolysis index is 7.2%, exceeding the 5% threshold. Discretisation error remains a gap at MRL 5. Achieved level 3 against required level 4."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
