      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental test conditions (flow rate, rotational speed, fluid temperature, hematocrit) must match COU operating envelope within stated uncertainty bounds.",
      "rationale": "Flow rate and rotational speed match COU envelope. Hematocrit in validation experiments was 33% vs. 40% target in COU; temperature deviation ±3 °C. Partial match achieved; level 3 against required level 4."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Output comparison",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative comparison metric (e.g., E_rel) computed with uncertainty; agreement within 15% MAE on hemolysis index across all operating points.",
      "rationale": "MAE of 12.4% meets the 15% threshold at nominal conditions, but two of five operating points show errors of 14.8% and 13.9% approaching the limit. Uncertainty in experimental reference adds ±4%. Achieved level 3 against required level 4 due to marginal operating-point coverage."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
