      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation QoI must be the absolute hemolysis index (not normalised or relative) directly used in the regulatory acceptance criterion.",
      "rationale": "Validation uses absolute HI consistent with the COU acceptance threshold. However, the sub-lethal platelet activation index, a secondary QoI required at MRL 5, has not been validated. Achieved level 3 against required level 4."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
