      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation activities must cover the full COU operating envelope (5 flow-speed combinations) with the same pump geometry and fluid properties used in the submission model.",
      "rationale": "Validation covers 4 of 5 COU operating points; the highest-speed point (6000 rpm, 6 L/min) was not included in the validation study due to experimental facility constraints. Achieved level 3 against required level 4."
    },
    {
