      "acceptanceCriteria": "Iterative convergence to residual < 1e-6 for all equations; floating-point round-off analysis documented.",
      "rationale": "Iterative residuals reported but floating-point sensitivity analysis not performed. Solver error quantification for the hemolysis scalar at MRL 5 requires formal round-off bounding; this has not been completed. Factor not assessed."
    },
