      "acceptanceCriteria": "Minimum three independent pump specimens tested; lot-to-lot variability in hemolysis characterised and incorporated into validation uncertainty budget.",
      "rationale": "Experimental data sourced from a single pump specimen. Lot-to-lot variability in hemolysis has not been characterised. Test-sample factor not assessed; epistemic gap at MRL 5."
