      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Formal equivalency mapping between validation experiment input parameters and COU input parameters, with documented bridging justification for any differences.",
      "rationale": "No formal equivalency mapping document produced. Differences in hematocrit and temperature between validation and COU have been noted qualitatively but not quantitatively bridged. Factor flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5."
