    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team accepted the package on the basis that seven of thirteen factors have been assessed and the primary validation metric (MAE 12.4%) meets the pre-specified 15% threshold. Six factors remain not-assessed or below required levels, representing acknowledged epistemic gaps consistent with the Low assurance level declaration. Re-validation of the 2025-Q3 rheology dataset against the revised model build is planned for Q2 2026 and is a condition of continued use.",
